{"tid":1659372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"#前線精選 【點解我地咁重視推翻政權？】","createTime":"2019-10-17T02:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T03:07:10.000Z","uid":34293,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"193a048ed09b7ee3153da02760d981c5fa42789b","tid":1659372,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:11:03.000Z","msg":"#前線精選 <br />\n//點解我地咁重視推翻政權？因為冇一個政權會放過一群：斬狗，搶槍，火魔，攻擊銀行鐵路既人，我地坐硬終身，唔洗打官司都知。就算爭取到讓步，輕判都最多由終身到10年咁解。<br />\n<br />\n而我地好明確，只要仲有一個兄弟要坐監，就算只係坐一兩年，我地都唔會停止攻擊或解散武裝， 齊上齊落係我地第一信條。打到今日，最前線係真正既無晒退路，對我地黎講，只有一路打上去推翻政權先係唯一生路，唔係勇武退場就冇事，停戰留港就等大搜捕坐一世，離港流亡我地聽最多真係4隻字 &ldquo;長貧難顧&rdquo; 。<br />\n<br />\n武裝革命係一條血路，但執起刀槍而死既人，會比自殺同被政權逼死既人少。//<br />\n<br />\n雖然篇幅比較長, 但一眾admin都好認同<br />\n希望大家可以花少少時間睇完佢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://telegra.ph/V小隊理論篇戰略篇戰術篇及行動升級預告-10-15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftelegra.ph%2FV%E5%B0%8F%E9%9A%8A%E7%90%86%E8%AB%96%E7%AF%87%E6%88%B0%E7%95%A5%E7%AF%87%E6%88%B0%E8%A1%93%E7%AF%87%E5%8F%8A%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E5%8D%87%E7%B4%9A%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A-10-15&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgBVENBC9VnKGSHAjWoGsWeM%3D&h=e0cce018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://telegra.ph/V小隊理論篇戰略篇戰術篇及行動升級預告-10-15</a>"},{"pid":"1646de74e3c313217a625789472d2e4d3f7ede57","tid":1659372,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:11:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7eLY27V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7eLY27V.jpg&h=0bfc2f6e&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"4410201c326fa77ed94ab59db4cdcdff23c9d36a","tid":1659372,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T02:11:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ad60fca8fc5eaa37a91a61bfbdd51b5a3ddfcd","tid":1659372,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4410201c326fa77ed94ab59db4cdcdff23c9d36a","tid":1659372,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,